oriam-segment-i-am-not-okay-1235775737/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Katie Atkinson]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Mon, 16 Sep 2024 02:44:29 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Awards]]></category><category><![CDATA[Music]]></category><category><![CDATA[Emmys]]></category><category><![CDATA[Music News]]></category><category><![CDATA[TV / Film]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?p=1235775737 </guid><description><![CDATA["I hope that this song can act as a healing moment for those mourning the storytellers that we have lost this year," Jelly says to introduce the performance.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> <a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/jelly-roll/"  >Jelly Roll</a>于周日晚上（9 月 15 日）首次亮相艾美奖，用他凄美的歌曲“I Am Not Excellent”为“纪念”部分配乐。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>当这位乡村音乐制作人登上洛杉矶孔雀剧院的舞台时，他介绍了自己的歌曲——迄今为止在<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/charts/hot-100/"  >公告牌百强单曲榜上</a>排名第 23 的单曲《 <em>Beautifully Broken</em> 》——他说：“我相信音乐是有治疗作用的。我相信音乐可以治愈。我也相信讲故事同样具有宣泄作用。我希望这首歌能够成为那些哀悼今年失去的讲故事者的人们的治愈时刻。如果今晚你感到失落或孤独，我想让你知道，不总是一切顺利也没关系。” </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img decoding="async" class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/jon-stewart-daily-show-emmys-2024-billboard-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/jon-stewart-daily-show-emmys-2024-billboard-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="2024 年 9 月 15 日，乔恩·斯图尔特（中）在洛杉矶 L.A. Live 孔雀剧院举行的第 76 届艾美奖颁奖典礼上，凭借《每日秀》在舞台上接受了杰出谈话系列奖。" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max"> 《每日秀》、约翰·奥利弗等人在 2024 年艾美奖颁奖典礼上大获全胜</h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"> 2024年9月15日</time></div></div></div><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>这位纳什维尔明星穿着全黑西装站在舞台中央，身后的弦乐部分增加了歌曲的情感分量。今年我们失去的一系列名人和面孔在《果冻卷》后面的大屏幕上滚动，其中包括理查德·西蒙斯、马丁·马尔、莎南·多尔蒂、卡尔·韦瑟斯、理查德·刘易斯、唐纳德·萨瑟兰和上周刚刚去世的詹姆斯·厄尔·琼斯。 93.</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>最终的名字和面孔是<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/lists/bob-newhart-billboard-awards-charts-history/"  >鲍勃·纽哈特 (Bob Newhart)</a> ，当吉米·金梅尔 (Jimmy Kimmel) 上台时，他留在屏幕上，干巴巴地打趣道：“我们最怀念的已故行业专业人士奖将颁给……”金梅尔接着向这位喜剧演员致敬。 ，他 1960 年的项目<em>《The Button-Down Mind of Bob Newhart》</em>是<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/lists/bob-newhart-billboard-awards-charts-history/"  >第一张登上 Billboard 200 排行榜第一名的喜剧专辑</a>。</p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 1235775737</post-id></item><item><title>凯西·贝茨 (Kathy Bates) 与安娜·萨瓦伊 (Anna Sawai) 的粉丝时刻，想与 Prince 等合作 | 2024 年艾美奖</title><link/>https://www.billboard.com/video/kathy-bates-fangirl-moment-with-anna-sawai-wanting-to-work-with-prince-emmy-awards-2024/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Katie Cao]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Mon, 16 Sep 2024 01:26:43 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Videos]]></category><category><![CDATA[2024 Emmy Awards]]></category><category><![CDATA[2024 Emmys]]></category><category><![CDATA[Billboard]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?post_type=pmc_top_video&amp;p=1235775726 </guid><description><![CDATA[Kathy Bates caught up with Billboard’s Tetris Kelly on the red carpet of the 2024 Emmy Awards.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-not-a-paywall"><p
